[DataRow(2L, "Bob")]
public void GetUserName_ReturnsCorrectName(int id, ...)

// Option A: change literals to int
[DataRow(1, "Alice")]
[DataRow(2, "Bob")]

// Option B: change parameter to long
public void GetUserName_ReturnsCorrectName(long id, ...)
```

**c) Timeout behavior** — `[Timeout(3000)]` on line 32 is still valid but behavior is now unified across platforms. Verify it still works as expected after migration.

